t | 正常态 |\n| No Avatar | `avatarUrl: null` |\n\n---\n\n## 4. 有机体组件（Orga
nisms）\n\n### 4.1 `SwipeCardStack`\n\n卡片堆叠容器，管理多层卡片渲染与手势冲突
。\n\n```dart\nimport \'package:flutter/material.dart\';\nimport \'../theme/toke
ns.dart\';\n\n/// 推荐卡片堆叠视图\nclass SwipeCardStack extends StatefulWidget 
{\n  /// 当前待展示的卡片数据列表（按展示顺序，index 0 为最顶层）\n  final List<
SwipeCardData> cards;\n\n  /// 用户向左滑（Pass）或点击 Pass 按钮时的回调\n  fin
al ValueChanged<String>? onPass;\n\n  /// 用户向右滑（Like）或点击 Like 按钮时的
回调\n  final ValueChanged<String>? onLike;\n\n  /// 当剩余卡片数少于 threshold 
时触发的预加载回调\n  final VoidCallback? onNeedMore;\n\n  /// 剩余卡片数触发预
加载的阈值（默认 3）\n  final int preloadThreshold;\n\n  /// 滑动判定阈值（默认 
120.0）\n  final double swipeThreshold;\n\n  /// 下层卡片的视觉参数\n  final dou
ble behindCardScale;\n  final double behindCardOffsetY;\n\n  const SwipeCardStac
k({\n    super.key,\n    required this.cards,\n    this.onPass,\n    this.onLike
,\n    this.onNeedMore,\n    this.preloadThreshold = 3,\n    this.swipeThreshold
= 120.0,\n    this.behindCardScale = 0.95,\n    this.behindCardOffsetY = 12.0,\n
 });\n\n  @override\n  State<SwipeCardStack> createState() => _SwipeCardStackSta
te();\n}\n\nclass SwipeCardData {\n  final String userId;\n  final String imageU
rl;\n  final String nickname;\n  final int age;\n  final String distance;\n  fin
al String lastActive;\n  final String? bio;\n\n  const SwipeCardData({\n    requ
ired this.userId,\n    required this.imageUrl,\n    required this.nickname,\n   
required this.age,\n    required this.distance,\n    required this.lastActive,\n
   this.bio,\n  });\n}\n\nclass _SwipeCardStackState extends State<SwipeCardStac
k> {\n  // 实现约束：\n  // - 手势识别：使用 GestureDetector（或 Draggable？）捕
获水平拖动\n  //   - 仅最顶层卡片响应手势\n  //   - 拖动时：transform = translat
eX(dx) + rotate(dx * 0.05°)\n  //   - 实时向 SwipeCard 传入 dragOffset，驱动 bad
ge 透明度\n  // - 释放判定：\n  //   - dx > swipeThreshold → 向右飞出屏幕（trans
lateX = +屏幕宽），触发 onLike(userId)\n  //   - dx < -swipeThreshold → 向左飞出
屏幕，触发 onPass(userId)\n  //   - 否则 → 弹性回弹动画（300ms, easeOutCubic）\n
 // - 飞出动画时长：300ms，曲线 Curves.easeOutCubic\n  // - 飞出后：从 cards 列
表移除该卡片，更新状态\n  // - 预加载：移除后若 cards.length < preloadThreshold
，调用 onNeedMore?.call()\n  // - 下层卡片：scale = behindCardScale, translateY 
= behindCardOffsetY，当顶层卡片飞出时，下层卡片在 300ms 内恢复 scale 1.0 / trans
lateY 0\n  // - 空状态：当 cards.isEmpty 时，显示一个占位 Container（不处理空状
态 UI，由外部 EmptyRecommendationView 接管）\n  // - 安全区：顶部避开 MediaQuery
.padding.top\n  @override\n  Widget build(BuildContext context) => const Placeho
lder();\n}\n```\n\n#### Widgetbook 用例要求\n\n| 用例名 | 状态组合 |\n|--------|
----------|\n| 3 Cards Stack | 传入 3 条数据，展示堆叠效果 |\n| 1 Card | 传入 1 
条数据 |\n| Empty | 传入空列表 |\n\n---\n\n### 4.2 `MatchSuccessDialog`\n\n配对
